    <reference type="string">&lt;div class="col-lg-9" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 802.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"&gt;
	&lt;div class="ContentText" style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;To access an Exchange mailbox from a non-Outlook client (e.g. from a UNIX/Linux PC) or an application inside the HP network,&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Exchange Web Services (EWS), POP3,&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;IMAP4&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;protocols are available.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;h2 class="RightModuleHeader" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px;"&gt;
			Exchange Web Services&lt;/h2&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;View&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/ITSArticle?ArticleNumber=000002494" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 125, 186); text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;font color="#0066cc" style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;EWS Autodiscover Information&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;h2 class="RightModuleHeader" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px;"&gt;
			POP3 or IMAP4&lt;/h2&gt;
		&lt;h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px;"&gt;
			&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Personal Mailbox:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;POP or IMAP Internal access&lt;/h3&gt;
		&lt;ul class="list" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; list-style: none;"&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 16px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 3px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
				"Incoming Mail"&amp;nbsp;server –&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;webmail.hp.com&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 16px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 3px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
				Incoming Mail server authentication
				&lt;ul class="indentList" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: none;"&gt;
					&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
						&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Account Name&lt;/b&gt;: Simplified Email Address, e.g.&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="mailto:joe.smith@hp.com" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 125, 186); text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;font color="#0066cc" size="2" style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;joe.smith@hp.com&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
						Password:&amp;nbsp;Your NT Domain password&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;/ul&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 16px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 3px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
				Use SSL -- you must use SSL for incoming mail, SSL ports are 993 for IMAP and 995 for POP3&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;ul class="list" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; list-style: none;"&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 16px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 3px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
				“Outgoing SMTP” server –&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;smtp3.hp.com&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 16px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 3px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
				Outgoing mail server authentication
				&lt;ul class="indentList" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: none;"&gt;
					&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
						&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Account Name&lt;/b&gt;:&amp;nbsp;Simplified Email Address, e.g.&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="mailto:joe.smith@hp.com" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 125, 186); text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;font color="#0066cc" size="2" style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;joe.smith@hp.com&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
						&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Password&lt;/b&gt;:&amp;nbsp;Your NT Domain Password&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;/ul&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 16px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 3px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
				Outgoing mail server&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;requires&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;authentication&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 16px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 3px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
				Outgoing mail does not require SSL&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px;"&gt;
			&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Process Mailbox:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;POP or IMAP Internal access&lt;/h3&gt;
		&lt;ol class="list" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; list-style: none;"&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 16px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 3px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
				Go to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="http://catalyst.hp.com/atm/" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 125, 186); text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" target="_blank" title=""&gt;&lt;font color="#0066cc" style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;ATM (Automated Technology Manager)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 16px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 3px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
				Add a normal user account as editor to the process mailbox&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 16px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 3px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
				Configure POP3 or IMAP access as follows:
				&lt;ul class="indentList" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: none;"&gt;
					&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
						“Incoming Mail” server –&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;webmail.hp.com&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
						Incoming Mail server authentication:
						&lt;ul class="indentList" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: none;"&gt;
							&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
								&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Account Name&lt;/b&gt;: &amp;lt;domain&amp;gt;/&amp;lt;username&amp;gt;/&amp;lt;alias name&amp;gt;
								&lt;ul class="indentList" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: none;"&gt;
									&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
										&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;alias name&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;= alias of the process mailbox, this info can be found in Outlook address book:
										&lt;ul class="indentList" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: none;"&gt;
											&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
												Open Outlook Address Book&lt;/li&gt;
											&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
												Search and select the process mailbox&lt;/li&gt;
											&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
												Double click the process mailbox to see detail information&lt;/li&gt;
											&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
												Alias name is in General tab&lt;/li&gt;
										&lt;/ul&gt;
									&lt;/li&gt;
									&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
										&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;domain &amp;amp; username&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;= the domain and username of the&amp;nbsp;account that has permission to open the process mailbox&lt;/li&gt;
								&lt;/ul&gt;
							&lt;/li&gt;
							&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
								&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Password&lt;/b&gt;:&amp;nbsp;NT Domain password of the user account that has permission to open the process mailbox&lt;/li&gt;
							&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
								&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Use SSL&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;- you must use SSL for incoming mail, SSL ports are 993 for IMAP and 995 for POP3&lt;/li&gt;
							&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
								Enable&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Log on using Secure Password Authentication&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
						&lt;/ul&gt;
					&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
						“Outgoing SMTP” server –&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;smtp3.com&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
						Outgoing mail server&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;does not&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;requires&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;authentication&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; margin: 0px; background: url(https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/resource/1411426972000/ITSimages/orangeArrow.png) 17px 0.55em no-repeat;"&gt;
						Outgoing mail does not require SSL&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;/ul&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ol&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;LDAP:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;You may configure your client to access HP's Enterprise Directory (see&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="http://directory.hp.com/support/ldap_ed_servers.html" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 125, 186); text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" target="_blank" title=""&gt;&lt;font color="#0066cc" style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;List of HP LDAP server names&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;). Also, set the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Search base&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;in your client to "&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;o=XX.com&lt;/strong&gt;".&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
